fails:
```scala
scala> def x[T <: Any { def +(t: Int): T }](t: T) = t + 2

scala> x(3)
java.lang.NoSuchMethodException ...
```

fails:
```scala
scala> def x[T](t: Any {def +(b: Int): T }) = t + 2

scala> x(5)
java.lang.NoSuchMethodException ...
```

works:
```scala
scala> def x[T <: Any { def +(t: Int): Int }](t: T) = t + 2

scala> x(3)
res0: Int = 5
```

works:
```scala
scala> def x(t: Any {def +(b: Int): Int }) = t + 2

scala> x(3)
res1: Int = 5
```
